{"tid":2501130,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人唔太欣賞LeBron呢種冇技術打法","createTime":"2021-04-23T07:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T09:50:39.000Z","uid":358892,"like":36,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9a50c66a0c4809c62c716ba13914ae67e7f67988","tid":2501130,"uid":358892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:04:36.000Z","msg":"雖然都打咗咁多年<br />\n破咗好多紀錄<br />\n但直到今日<br />\n都仲係覺得佢呢種打法係無技術<br />\n純粹基因勁身體質素屈機畀佢生到6 ft 9 250lbs 垂直彈跳43吋又跑得快<br />\n一尾爆爆爆<br />\n咁大份人仲要成日flop<br />\n贏就佢功勞<br />\n輸就隊友廢教練廢<br />\n呢個打法較欠缺說服力<br />\n<br />\n純討論佢打波技術層面<br />\n佢場下奶共奶到成隻狗咁<br />\n又成日tweet埋啲鳩嘢扮政治英雄<br />\n仲話自己好educated呢啲我都唔講<br />\n占屎大帝 Fans唔好屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ae30907e7d653340c9179b2e08d7e6eb608f63","tid":2501130,"uid":130445,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:09:22.000Z","msg":"想講好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFree throw 勁差又成日flop"},{"pid":"77245edeb5ef98803ec981df807226ac74f59c02","tid":2501130,"uid":9,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:09:56.000Z","msg":"好似下下硬爆咁<br />\n同隧友無乜組織<br />\n佢有時仲會遊魂"},{"pid":"36fbf8fa27c21336b4562b5b89bdf9f465435d33","tid":2501130,"uid":318164,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:10:09.000Z","msg":"靠AD carry"},{"pid":"adff49493f65a14797cc44e96ef1845da4329b7a","tid":2501130,"uid":154978,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:10:56.000Z","msg":"本身都覺係，但見到字母哥仲係打到成碌柒咁<br />\n都不得不佩服阿奶嗰分波同IQ<br />\n佢好知道佢剷入去嗰下啲人會企係邊<br />\n<br />\n得分手段都唔係最top<br />\n所以拍住Wade同Irving會好好<br />\n<br />\n可惜阿奶有陣嗰腦短路"},{"pid":"76b1478d9c07f788b69ba1cd2465cc8e24c42855","tid":2501130,"uid":57462,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:11:35.000Z","msg":"起碼傳球係技術掛...助攻王<br />\n你話佢ball control 冇MJ KI Curry 咁勁係認同既，但我諗佢唔係top姐，未至於冇<br />\n<br />\n如果身體係override 所有野，咁大家睇physical attribution draft 人就得"},{"pid":"9d11bc700a6cf580921f1c37350ac4cf03fb8863","tid":2501130,"uid":358892,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:17:08.000Z","msg":"聽到而家啲人完全直接skip咗Kobe<br />\n甚至話已經超越Jordan<br />\n話佢係GOAT就想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇破紀錄來講佢係真係好可能史上第一嘅<br />\n但係睇技術<br />\n同Kobe Jordan比<br />\n唔係差小小<br />\n係講梗差幾皮<br />\nMentality同attitude仲垃圾<br />\n人哋Kobe Jordan係好有鬥心<br />\n畀人hack就發嬲爆返人<br />\nJames條友咁嘅身體質素<br />\n就flop flop flop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要load management<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aecdfc2c7b9a6d204dd3373cd981e15bec8a1b8","tid":2501130,"uid":32220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:18:57.000Z","msg":"其實係佢身體質素太勁太大舊攪到佢啲動作好似好怪咁姐，其實佢啲視野係好"},{"pid":"947f9f7b0d1a25fc8e2eb7d4309a9f306e9f7b5e","tid":2501130,"uid":28193,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:20:13.000Z","msg":"咁ZION WILLIAMSON叫咩........."},{"pid":"cfa53ea5a818a00bffc8187f9c38c2c3f5e9933b","tid":2501130,"uid":396090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77245edeb5ef98803ec981df807226ac74f59c02","tid":2501130,"uid":9,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:09:56.000Z","msg":"好似下下硬爆咁<br />\n同隧友無乜組織<br />\n佢有時仲會遊魂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:20:28.000Z","msg":"無組織？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif